song.title: Space Pop
song.info:
Ranked #6 place in the Music Contest 6 (veteran division). [url=https://hornet.org/ha/pages/mc6/results_2/veteran/m6v-spop.html]MC6 ratings on this track! :D[/url]
Simple yet tracked one, but I loved it. The melodies are nice, you might expect it out of tune a bit.. however it's good imho.
Note: The final version of this track is longer than this one, so this uploaded one here is shortened for the compo. :P
